step:
1: download languages xpi files example
wget -r ftp://ftp.mozilla.org/pub/mozilla.org/thunderbird/releases/17.0.8/linux-i686/xpi/

2: open xpi files with ark

3: give the command

for j in * ; do mv "$j" "langpack-$j@thunderbird.mozilla.org"; done

4: drop the files to langpack-tb


6: tar cJvf thunderbird-l10n-17.0.8.tar.xz --exclude=.hgtags --exclude=.hgignore --exclude=.hg --exclude=browser --exclude=calendar --exclude=suite langpack-tb

supported

